your organization to directors, and

54
00:02:18.321 --> 00:02:21.170
VPs, and even the executives sometimes.

55
00:02:21.170 --> 00:02:25.099
You speak for an entire group of people.

56
00:02:25.099 --> 00:02:28.464
That's something you'll do in your
role as an engineering manager.

57
